description: This course covers every step needed to rank a live event on the first page of Google. All videos are a look over my shoulder screen capture as I set up all the steps needed to rank your Live Event. After taking this course you will be able to apply the same strategy to rank your own live events and get traffic to your videos. This course was made for beginners in mind and is easy to follow along. This is the perfect SEO course for you if you want to rank in Google fast and not wait months to see results
title: How To Use Google Hangouts to Rank In Google Introductory
